@startuml UC09_sequence
title UC09 - Quan ly thong tin ca nhan
actor "Khach hang" as Customer
boundary "ProfilePage" as ProfilePage
control "CustomerProfileController" as ProfileController
control "ProfileService" as ProfileService
control "PasswordEncoder" as PasswordEncoder
database "UserRepository / users" as UserRepo

Customer -> ProfilePage : Mo trang Tai khoan
ProfilePage -> ProfileController : GET /api/customer/profile
ProfileController -> ProfileService : getProfile(username)
ProfileService -> UserRepo : findByUsername(username)
UserRepo --> ProfileService : User
ProfileService --> ProfileController : ProfileResponse
ProfileController --> ProfilePage : Hien thi thong tin hien tai

Customer -> ProfilePage : Sua fullName/email/phone/address
Customer -> ProfilePage : (Tuy chon) nhap currentPassword + newPassword
Customer -> ProfilePage : Bam nut Luu thay doi
ProfilePage -> ProfileController : PUT /api/customer/profile
ProfileController -> ProfileService : updateProfile(username,request)
ProfileService -> UserRepo : findByUsername(username)
opt Doi mat khau
  ProfileService -> PasswordEncoder : matches(currentPassword, oldHash)
  ProfileService -> PasswordEncoder : encode(newPassword)
end
ProfileService -> UserRepo : save(User)
ProfileService --> ProfileController : ProfileResponse moi
ProfileController --> ProfilePage : 200 + thong bao cap nhat thanh cong

alt Email trung / currentPassword sai / du lieu khong hop le
  ProfileService --> ProfileController : IllegalArgumentException
  ProfileController --> ProfilePage : 400 + thong bao loi
  ProfilePage --> Customer : Hien thi loi
else Loi CSDL
  UserRepo --> ProfileService : DataAccessException
  ProfileController --> ProfilePage : 500 Loi he thong
  ProfilePage --> Customer : Hien thi Loi he thong
end
@enduml
